{"tid":409818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又炒車）英國律師監管當局再回覆《立場》　稱有\"Kwan Yiu Ho\"名字註冊","createTime":"2017-09-22T11:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T01:23:49.000Z","uid":41351,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7027bed09ebafe61f7de33edcf4caba03f396d3","tid":409818,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"今早流傳一封信件，指立法會議員何君堯「英格蘭和威爾士執業律師」資格存疑一事，《立場新聞》致電被指發出信件的英國Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA)。該局職員回覆稱，由於缺乏信件參考編號，無法確認香港流傳的信件真偽（有關信件的參考編號被遮蔽）。該局職員應《立場》記者要求即時翻查「英國和威爾士執業律師」名冊，以多個名字組合仍然找不到何君堯的名字。其後該局再回覆立場記者，指查到有&quot;Kwan Yiu Ho&quot;一名字，在1997年9月1日註冊。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯早前回覆《立場新聞》及在FB直播解畫時指，自己曾於英國和新加坡兩地註冊，只是沒有執業，故其名字未能在SRA名冊中顯示。不過，SRA職員回覆立場新聞時表示，只要曾經註冊（admitted），無論有否在當地執業，名冊均會有所紀錄，並應有SRA ID number。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E4%BD%86%E6%9F%A5%E7%84%A1-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E6%AD%A4%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A8%25BB%25E5%2586%258A%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=da709eab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25A8%25BB%25E5%2586%258A%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%2584%25A1-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0