3653_85378bee7a898ac69f1b1efaae8c1fe5.jpg&h=f8809293&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有執業律師資格同有無執過業無矛盾bor<br />\n佢的確係有英國執業律師牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCert都冇叫做有資格？<br />\n<br />\n自己又認左冇<br />\n<br />\n人地官方執業律師database又冇<br />\n<br />\n算鳩數啦你</blockquote><br />\nSolicitors Regulation Authority  已證實搵到佢既登記，即係已經具英國執業資格牌<br />\n你可以話佢無係英國執過業，但要拗執業律師資格就講唔通<br />\nJR佢都無可能告得入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰個係駐册紀錄戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，一定係何生夢遊時執業<br />\n<br />\n佢唔知英國公會唔知得你知啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw冇cert執業都係犯法啦戇鳩"},{"pid":"974412108790bf247050688d73333f795c7e36c1","tid":409818,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"香港01:英律師會：何君堯從無申請「執業」　履歷卻稱任英國執業律師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/409855/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/409855/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9e638333eb0a3ce68355dc4a7ceb0a3f7695dcb","tid":409818,"uid":60432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姓關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學雞番去温書喇"},{"pid":"feed5e7933e798d17b5c07ab74f5435cac93c87c","tid":409818,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61eacae1476f0963d3bf300226140aea5897c79","tid":409818,"uid":43189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"睇下五毛開post開得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124f7ace3ddac0275f409569c47e2de6559f9da2","tid":409818,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"炒咩車，有名=可以做野"},{"pid":"11853e42217d1809c043af789ec39dc09780a9ae","tid":409818,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"sra只係證實牛屎佬曾經係97年9月1日係佢哋度註冊<br />\n但冇證明佢有keep住每年renewal佢個practising certificate<br />\n係每年都要<br />\n所以佢唔係冇執業 佢係根本冇得執業<br />\n佢自己都認咗 仲幫佢兜做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c016770f8310a9b5dacf05a5c2a413b0ec814494","tid":409818,"uid":18725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"&quot;但現時沒有他的「執業律師」登記，亦從未收過何的「執業律師」申請證書。&quot;"},{"pid":"0e40adfc40575695d31bd27740e107c0773b7cea","tid":409818,"uid":34144,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有註冊，無執業<br />\n何君堯自己認左冇執業資格<br />\n無practising cert<br />\n唔洗再討論哩個point<br />\n2:00開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/1504411756318341/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJuniusHoKwanYiu%2Fvideos%2F1504411756318341%2F&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c7656312\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/1504411756318341/</a><br />\n<br />\n但選舉宣傳自稱英國執業律師<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/193653_85378bee7a898ac69f1b1efaae8c1fe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F193653_85378bee7a898ac69f1b1efaae8c1fe5.jpg&h=f8809293&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有執業律師資格同有無執過業無矛盾bor<br />\n佢的確係有英國執業律師牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCert都冇叫做有資格？<br />\n<br />\n自己又認左冇<br />\n<br />\n人地官方執業律師database又冇<br />\n<br />\n算鳩數啦你</blockquote><br />\nSolicitors Regulation Authority  已證實搵到佢既登記，即係已經具英國執業資格牌<br />\n你可以話佢無係英國執過業，但要拗執業律師資格就講唔通<br />\nJR佢都無可能告得入</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n訓醒未啊柒頭<br />\n<br />\n根據英國Solicitors Act 1974（執業律師條例1974），任何人以事務律師（Solicitor）行事，須符合三個資格，當中包括了合資格的「執業證書（practising certificate）」<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞》記者翻查英國法例《Solicitors Act》，條文列明以事務律師（Solicitor）行事（act）須符合三個資格，包括登記為事務律師、在事務律師名冊上，並有合資格的「執業證書（practising certificate）」。執業律師條例同時規定，任何不符資格的人士，宣稱自己作為（act as ）事務律師，也屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n佢冇 practising cert, 即係佢不能執業,唔係不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f53a462a000efda8fd645c72b0a944d7fcc868","tid":409818,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"今次英國佬彈弓手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1778be4fffba30b60e39ea68a4f44627958e21","tid":409818,"uid":8009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"呢個樓主五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7235a975f8fff88dd036c3b56834e80c2b11fd7b","tid":409818,"uid":83582,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個樓主五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻五毛專做標題黨, 有時文不對題"},{"pid":"f80c2d28ca9f2ed98f565eeefe92d8b328472546","tid":409818,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有註冊，無執業<br />\n何君堯自己認左冇執業資格<br />\n無practising cert<br />\n唔洗再討論哩個point<br />\n2:00開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/1504411756318341/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJuniusHoKwanYiu%2Fvideos%2F1504411756318341%2F&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=c7656312\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JuniusHoKwanYiu/videos/1504411756318341/</a><br />\n<br />\n但選舉宣傳自稱英國執業律師<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/